					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12469643#post-4350719</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12469643/scp-4052#post-4350719</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2019 15:22:20 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Deadly Bread</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3988532</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm happy you liked it! I've condensed the addendum a bit by removing some of the experiments while still hopefully making it clear how the officer is getting fed up. I've kept the letter about the same length because I still feel that most of its contents are important.</p> <p>Thank you both for your advice.</p> 
				 	]]>
